INSERT INTO email_trigger (
                workspace_id,
                path,
                script_path,
                is_flow,
                local_part,
                workspaced_local_part,
                edited_by,
                email,
                edited_at,
                error_handler_path,
                error_handler_args,
                retry,
                mode
            ) VALUES (
                $1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7, $8, now(), $9, $10, $11, $12
            )
